{"tid":640535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有餅咩都得] 黃子華棟篤笑門票開售 長者購票後即轉交他人","createTime":"2018-04-24T10:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T10:58:37.000Z","uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf84d9862c95711ef050d872a738064ea30313d","tid":640535,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=303479&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D303479%26refer%3Dshare&d=PIhFHYhkq2G3Nufb4QOKIbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=2b80c19b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D303479%26refer%3Dshare&h=18edc2cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=303479&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】黃子華棟篤笑門票今天公開發售，有人通宵排隊購票。前來購票的市民稱有人以紙皮霸位，更見到有很多「蛇頭」帶公公婆婆到來排隊。<br />\n<br />\n門票公開發售前一晚，尖沙咀文化中心外人龍足足繞了一個圈，他們乾脆在紙皮上「打地鋪」。<br />\n<br />\n到早上一度有幾百人排隊。公公婆婆「擔凳仔」，三五成群坐在一起；驟眼看人龍，「最棒場」的似乎是一眾公公婆婆。<br />\n<br />\n一群婆婆購票後走到售票處旁圍着一個穿淺藍色外套的女人，婆婆將信封交給她，信封內裝着的是門票，他們之後結伴離開。<br />\n<br />\n成功買到門票的胡先生稱，星期一晚十時來排隊，有人以紙皮霸位，更見到有很多「蛇頭」帶公公婆婆到來排隊。<br />\n<br />\n文化中心派員維持秩序，又向排隊的人派籌，但不限派籌次數，換言之，排隊的人可領取後再排隊領籌。<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀金馬倫道的售票處一樣見到人龍，售票處「墟冚」，網上亦有湧現黃牛票。<br />\n<br />\n棟篤笑門票原本最貴880元，但這個內地網上平台，標價八千多元的門票也有，另一個門票二手平台則賣逾千元。"},{"pid":"2c70061f12ce3b480226da5d74235d14f90657f1","tid":640535,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10b686c1a0f70df04422e46f162b9e0322c9724","tid":640535,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81cd969c625bc4c66b678b11dfaeec003d971a36","tid":640535,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 社會害蟲"},{"pid":"cd50dae815474e5e6d63984cc8af0ba447af08aa","tid":640535,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a10b686c1a0f70df04422e46f162b9e0322c9724","tid":640535,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔可以咁話老友記 佢地真係有餅咩都得"}]}